{
  "stem": "15017.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm, I'm, I'm now with the 50th RTR Regiment, and my number is Trooper Gilbert Zed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, in England, you don't say 'zee,' you say 'zed.'",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Trooper Gilbert Z, number 7918911, 50th Royal Tank Regiment, 7th Armored Brigade.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were sent out as reinforcements to join the 8th Army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at that time, the tanks and everything was coming in from America [HEBREW], everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we had to sail, and we didn't go by the Mediterranean.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went right round Africa, right up Aden, right up the Red Sea, to Port Said.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from there-- and I was stationed at the, at the regiment that we were acclimatized to being in, in Egypt, at [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the name of the camp, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, I was at El Alamein all the way through, as I showed you on the map.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in, it was in 19-- 1972.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fool.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the American Second Army came in from the other side under General Mark Clark with Patton and the others.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then it was a cake bomb.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, the Germans, as what could, we took a lot of prisoners.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And out of all the panzers that Germany had in the desert, there was only 15 left.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All the others were shot to pieces.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, we followed through to Sicily and then into Italy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was-- you know-- I was at Salerno and then later at Anzio.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was in July of 1944 that Rome had fallen, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But in the meantime-- one of the-- D-Day was June 6, 1944-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] just before then, one of the last V2s unfortunately killed my wife.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Luckily, my daughter was in school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was informed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was given compassionate leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
